          <tr><td><strong>Ireland</strong></td><td>Graduate density &amp; ICT/STEM fields</td><td>58% attainment (#2 overall); high master&rsquo;s/doctoral share; strong in ICT</td><td>OECD EAG 2025</td></tr>
